    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for a dependable, well-maintained ride? This good-condition vehicle is a fantastic find for anyone seeking reliability and everyday comfort! It drives smoothly and presents well cosmetically, with normal wear consistent with its age. The mechanicals are in solid shape, making this a trustworthy choice for commuters and families alike. Don't miss out on this genuinely well-kept car at a great value!",
